08c85e9b86","tid":113980,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過曬返黑</blockquote><br />\n曬唔黑，天生，無用任何護膚品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以勸各位絲打唔好再買美白產品，真係哂氣"},{"pid":"11cb93e4c9a4036311626fce174c38516abd14ac","tid":113980,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有 friend 係咁，成個歐洲人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實呢啲係咪真係基因問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講，我雙親家族個邊都係白，老母四川人，佢地親戚個邊多數白帶黃，我白帶紅，係室內or白燈睇落會覺得我發光"},{"pid":"f2b5e0905274234fbadb4cb6cb34cba8c94ad68c","tid":113980,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"圖都無張"},{"pid":"37d35c767bd54c786e08fa0b2309bcb967bc26c0","tid":113980,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪成日無街出</blockquote><br />\n日頭無街出，夜晚先有街出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連份工都係夜晚"}]}